【NEW】2015/01/13


自2015年起，華語文聽力、閱讀測驗入門基礎級正式考試將各新增一個題型，聽力測驗新增題型為「對話」，閱讀測驗增設「閱讀理解」題型。[入門基礎級測驗題型變更說明]
                In 2015, TOCFL's Listening and Reading Tests on Band A will each adopt an additional section of test items. There will be a Dialogue section in the Listening Test and a Reading Comprehension section in the Reading Test.[Updates to Test Section Addition in the TOCFL Band A]





